  "detailed_description": "Glitch of the Game is an indie rpg/puzzle game where you are the RPG Hero out to save your dog from The Big Bad. Unfortunately The Big Bad is so insanely overpowered he is impossible to defeat... unless you are able to figure out some glitches you might be able to exploit.<br><br>10 different glitches to find, such as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Infinite money<br></li><li>Fake walls<br></li><li>Integer overflows<br></li><li>Secret codes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.poster.avif?t=1722099348\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.webm?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.mp4?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The glitches are inspired by some of the most famous glitches and exploits from gaming's history - can you find them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.poster.avif?t=1722099348\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.webm?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.mp4?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Glitch of the Game is an indie rpg/puzzle game where you are the RPG Hero out to save your dog from The Big Bad. Unfortunately The Big Bad is so insanely overpowered he is impossible to defeat... unless you are able to figure out some glitches you might be able to exploit.<br><br>10 different glitches to find, such as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Infinite money<br></li><li>Fake walls<br></li><li>Integer overflows<br></li><li>Secret codes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.poster.avif?t=1722099348\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.webm?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/7c4f86864a505e555e5686b3b0d6e81c.mp4?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The glitches are inspired by some of the most famous glitches and exploits from gaming's history - can you find them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.poster.avif?t=1722099348\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.webm?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083650/extras/45838b7b932de7aa03643248eea9741f.mp4?t=1722099348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
